{"tid":1398922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解無人提檢控人員既公開信。這信如果係事實可以ko 律政司","createTime":"2019-08-03T03:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T05:31:38.000Z","uid":188522,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bed3291a527c56da4d494f2cc5e6df756dfb473f","tid":1398922,"uid":188522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:50:21.000Z","msg":"【律政司一批檢控人員發公開信  批評鄭若驊及梁卓然沒把好關】<br />\n<br />\n律政司一批檢控人員繼早前聯署後，再發公開信，批評律政司司長鄭若驊，及刑事檢控專員梁卓然，沒有做好把關，處理涉及大型公眾活動的案件時，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">主要考慮政治因素，沒有充份證據仍堅持檢控</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞 #公開信 #律政司 #刑事檢控科 #鄭若驊 #梁卓然<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1171538819704851?s=1021181400&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F186040714921338%2Fposts%2F1171538819704851%3Fs%3D1021181400%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDfkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=9600b69f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1171538819704851?s=1021181400&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1021181400/posts/10217427104402484?s=1021181400&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1021181400%2Fposts%2F10217427104402484%3Fs%3D1021181400%26sfns%3Dmo&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDfkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=1d01890f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1021181400/posts/10217427104402484?s=1021181400&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"0aeb0680728a1cf7724b44a333ce0ffbc13708af","tid":1398922,"uid":798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:07:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e304f0eda4bab66f22835664622cc0ac73c013e0","tid":1398922,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"423c07c0d78fe74720ab02a460da9916fc87ad0